143
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:21,910
Katanya situasi telah berubah.
Minta kita pindah stok ke area lain.

144
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:22,760
Pindahkan stok?

145
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:23,150
Iya.

146
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,880
Di tengah malam ini,
stok sepenting itu,...

147
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,110
...bagaimana bisa dipindah?

148
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:26,520
Ini...

149
00:13:26,520 --> 00:13:27,300
Aku juga tidak tahu.

150
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:31,790
Cepat pindahkan stok ke perahu
di dermaga nomor empat.

151
00:13:32,030 --> 00:13:33,550
Perahu Richu Kunshan.

152
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:16,440
Mana orangnya?

153
00:14:16,640 --> 00:14:17,540
Apakah sudah dikirim?

154
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,030
Pengurus Zhao.

155
00:14:19,350 --> 00:14:20,210
Aku mencari Tuan Zhao.

156
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:22,280
Kami mendapat telegram di dermaga.

157
