176
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:14,550
Mari.

177
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:16,020
Perlahan-lahan.

178
00:15:16,110 --> 00:15:17,060
Perhatikan langkahmu.

179
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:17,910
Baik.

180
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,200
Mari, letakkan di sini.

181
00:15:27,110 --> 00:15:28,350
Sesuatu terjadi pada Tuan Zhao.

182
00:15:28,710 --> 00:15:29,590
Aku tahu.

183
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:30,790
Lekas susun barangnya.

184
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:32,590
Aku bergegas mengunjunginya.

185
00:15:32,590 --> 00:15:35,030
Kau ini ternyata pandai
berpura-pura juga.

186
00:15:38,230 --> 00:15:39,760
Percepat kerjaan kalian. Cepat!

187
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:41,880
Cepat.

188
00:15:51,670 --> 00:15:52,870
Mereka sudah memindahkannya.

189
00:15:58,590 --> 00:16:00,080
Bisa mulai langkah selanjutnya.

190
00:16:39,280 --> 00:16:40,230
Ini...

191
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:42,000
Tuan Zhao.

192
00:16:42,150 --> 00:16:43,520
Bukankah Anda terluka?

193
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:46,150
Kenapa kalian di sini?

194
00:16:46,150 --> 00:16:47,760
Bukankah kuminta kalian
awasi stok?

195
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,640
Kudengar Tuan Zhao
alami kecelakaan,...

196
00:16:49,710 --> 00:16:52,280
...khusus mengikuti instruksimu
pindahkan stok ke tempat aman.

197
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:54,030
Kapan aku terluka?

198
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:56,960
Siapa yang minta kalian
pindahkan stok? Pindahkan ke mana?

199
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:58,880
