telepon ekstensi di kamar.

223
00:17:53,350 --> 00:17:56,310
Anda akan mendengarnya
jika telepon berdering.

224
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:06,560
Temukan.

225
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:10,110
